<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī saṁgamēsvaradēvara
<lb n="2"/>dibya śrīpāda pammārā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dhakarumappa muṁmu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḍi siṁgeyanayakana
<lb n="5"/>komara vīra kaṁpiladēva
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nu taṁma tayi mādānā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kiti siṁgeyanayaka perume
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ya nayaka <g type="danda">.</g> Iṁtu mūva
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ra liṁga pratiṣṭeya maḍisi
<lb n="10" break="no"/>da sivālya <g type="danda">.</g>
